===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|uncountable}} Rule by the people, especially as a form of [[government]]; either directly or through elected representatives ([[representative democracy]]).
#* '''1866''', J. Arthur Partridge, ''On Democracy'', Trübner & Co., page 2:
